  "detailed_description": "<h1>Early Access</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Game is  now V1.0. A Better Translation is now available！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for your support!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inkbrush & Blade — A Journey Through Mystic China</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>When spirits roam and legends come alive, only a true cultivator can restore balance.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a lone Yao Hunter, wield blade and spell to cleanse a world where ancient demons awaken and forgotten myths take shape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a hand-painted realm inspired by Chinese folklore — a living scroll of monsters, miracles, and martial arts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Every choice writes a legend. Every battle bends fate.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Path: Become a Legendary Yao Hunter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mo San</strong> – A warrior from the  Yao-Slaying Bureau, carrying a cursed blade thirsts  blood. <br>He channels his rage into raw power — but with every cut, the blade hungers more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long before it devours him whole?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915510/extras/8ad97d51b80189292064928c5d20f450.poster.avif?t=1762984919\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915510/extras/8ad97d51b80189292064928c5d20f450.webm?t=1762984919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chuan</strong> – A Taoist with a bamboo-fire sword and a pouch full of dangerous inventions. <br>He may look frail, but his bullets are blessed with talismanic magic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >His homemade weapons  \"Bamboo Bombard\" — turn spiritual alchemy into explosive justice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915510/extras/7decfc32ec92619e9ea030a5bde6ac6f.poster.avif?t=1762984919\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915510/extras/7decfc32ec92619e9ea030a5bde6ac6f.webm?t=1762984919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A-Zi</strong> – A prodigy witch from the southern Miao tribes, bonded with the poisons of the wild.<br>She commands a legion of venomous insects and conjures ancient hexes passed down through bloodlines. To fight her is to fight the jungle itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915510/extras/10850521cfe661ed39fe26ab987098e7.poster.avif?t=1762984919\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915510/extras/10850521cfe661ed39fe26ab987098e7.webm?t=1762984919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ao Yu</strong> – A young dragon-descendant learning to command the storm.<br>With mastery over wind, fire, thunder, and rain, she dances on the edge of control. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But when her human form shatters... the dragon within awakens.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915510/extras/ad713ab1df0fe6a446f4907abe5506dd.poster.avif?t=1762984919\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915510/extras/ad713ab1df0fe6a446f4907abe5506dd.webm?t=1762984919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>A Martial Fantasy Roguelike Rooted in Eastern Lore</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >400+ Handcrafted Cards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >172 Inner Skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >54 Mystical Elixirs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ Random Events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ Unique Enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 Ascending Difficulty Levels</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modes of Play</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yao Hunt Tournament</strong> – Team up with friends and race to cleanse the land</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yao-Hunter’s Edict</strong> – Daily global challenges with ranked leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Custom Mode</strong> – Tailor your adventure with custom seeds and rules</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steam Workshop Now Available!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the <strong>[Experimental Features → Workshop]</strong> menu to install community mods and create your own martial myths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Official Discord:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inkbrush & Blade — A Journey Through Mystic China</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>When spirits roam and legends come alive, only a true cultivator can restore balance.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a lone Yao Hunter, wield blade and spell to cleanse a world where ancient demons awaken and forgotten myths take shape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a hand-painted realm inspired by Chinese folklore — a living scroll of monsters, miracles, and martial arts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Every choice writes a legend. Every battle bends fate.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Path: Become a Legendary Yao Hunter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mo San</strong> – A warrior from the  Yao-Slaying Bureau, carrying a cursed blade thirsts  blood. <br>He channels his rage into raw power — but with every cut, the blade hungers more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long before it devours him whole?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915510/extras/8ad97d51b80189292064928c5d20f450.poster.avif?t=1762984919\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915510/extras/8ad97d51b80189292064928c5d20f450.webm?t=1762984919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chuan</strong> – A Taoist with a bamboo-fire sword and a pouch full of dangerous inventions. <br>He may look frail, but his bullets are blessed with talismanic magic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >His homemade weapons  \"Bamboo Bombard\" — turn spiritual alchemy into explosive justice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsi