al Fantasy Roguelike Rooted in Eastern Lore</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >400+ Handcrafted Cards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >172 Inner Skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >54 Mystical Elixirs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ Random Events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ Unique Enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 Ascending Difficulty Levels</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modes of Play</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yao Hunt Tournament</strong> – Team up with friends and race to cleanse the land</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yao-Hunter’s Edict</strong> – Daily global challenges with ranked leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Custom Mode</strong> – Tailor your adventure with custom seeds and rules</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steam Workshop Now Available!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the <strong>[Experimental Features → Workshop]</strong> menu to install community mods and create your own martial myths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Official Discord:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
